{"data":[{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"0_1733540966.765689","card_id":"Q_6100601022","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":6100601022,"title":"如何评价极客湾关于华为mate70pro+的测评？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/6100601022","type":"question","created":1733447184,"answer_count":221,"follower_count":542,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[3309592],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkEIs8349Pi85d9HEAMaCTExMjE5Njk1MSCQnMm6BjAAOJ4EQAByCjYxMDA2MDEwMjJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"638 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-e0b1c45ca7ba735d26ea869ecb970ff3_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"1_1733540966.767052","card_id":"Q_6137589259","target":{"id":6137589259,"title":"超级富豪黄仁勋被曝避税 80 亿美元，暴露出美国税制存在哪些问题？其行为会对美国社会造成什么影响？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/6137589259","type":"question","created":1733476144,"answer_count":230,"follower_count":545,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[472,6944,12573,1900043,3552115],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"凤凰网科技讯 北京时间12月6日，据《纽约时报》报道，作为世界超级富豪，英伟达CEO黄仁勋(Jensen Huang)利用美国联邦遗产税和赠与税中广为人知的漏洞避税，金额有望达到80亿美元。 黄仁勋目前净资产为1270亿美元(约合9227亿元人民币)，是美国第十大富豪。从理论上讲，当他去世时，他的遗产应该被征税，税款为其净资产的40%。 然而，现年61岁的黄仁勋不仅是一位工程天才和硅谷传奇，他还是一系列避税策略的受益者。根据《纽约时报》查阅的证券和税务文件，这些避税策略将能够让黄仁勋在不需要缴税的情况下将大部分财富传给他的家族。 《纽约时报》称，这些避税策略有望为其家族节省税款大约80亿美元，这很可能是美国规模最大的避税案例之一。 其实，黄仁勋采取的这套保护财富的策略在超级富豪中十分普遍。根据《纽约时报》对证券披露文件的分析，黑石集团创始人苏世民(Stephen A. Schwarzman)、Meta CEO马克·扎克伯格(Mark Zuckerberg)以及谷歌、Coinbase、礼来制药、万事达卡和AMD等公司的高管们，都将数以十亿美元计的资金转入金融工具，以规避联邦遗产税。 形同虚设的遗产税 美国联邦遗产税只针对该国一小部分超级富豪征收，但是黄仁勋等富豪的案例表明，这个税种已经形同虚设。自2000年以来，美国遗产税的收入几乎没有变化，而美国最富有阶层的财富却大约翻了两番。如果遗产税的收入与富豪们的财富增长保持同步，那么去年应征收大约1200亿美元的税款。然而，实际收入只有这个数字的四分之一左右。 这些流失的税收收入足以同时将美国司法部的预算提高一倍，并将用于癌症和阿尔茨海默症研究的联邦资金增加两倍。身家9000多亿，黄仁勋是如何避税的？"},"attached_info":"CkEIs8349Pi85d9HEAMaCTExMjIwNDM5MyCw/sq6BjAAOKEEQAFyCjYxMzc1ODkyNTl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"456 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-d5dd6b636148f2755df9bc0e859e80fd_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"2_1733540966.768385","card_id":"Q_1583625596","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":1583625596,"title":"当年苏联挖地球为什么挖到 12262 米就停止了？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/1583625596","type":"question","created":1729499975,"answer_count":189,"follower_count":1000,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[3298,10715],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkEIs8349Pi85d9HEAMaCTExMTI5MzQ2MSDHpti4BjAAOOgHQAJyCjE1ODM2MjU1OTZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"371 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-93423af8f333af5df5f179a26e586236_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"3_1733540966.769397","card_id":"Q_6144254296","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":6144254296,"title":"张勇不再任哪吒汽车 CEO，转任公司顾问，如何看待这一变化？目前哪吒汽车经营情况如何？","url":"https://api.zhihu.